The paper discusses the challenges and scenarios related to security and privacy in the context of technology and the internet. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Other likely categories include cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
